videos.headline: Holton Ahlers finds Audie Omotosho to tie the game late for Houston
videos.description: Holton Ahlers with a 13-yard touchdown pass to Audie Omotosho to tie the game up at 24-24.

videos.headline: Houston survives to topple East Carolina in OT
videos.description: Alton McCaskill runs in a touchdown on the first play of overtime and a forced fumble by Donovan Mutin helps Houston finally put away East Carolina 30-24.
